Regulatory Disclosures | Marshall Wace






















      Marshall Wace
    






Regulatory Disclosures
Marshall Wace conducts its business to meet the requirements of all appropriate regulatory authorities.

Marshall Wace LLP is authorised and regulated by the UK Financial Conduct Authority (“FCA”).
Marshall Wace North America LP is registered with the US Securities & Exchange Commission (“SEC”).
Marshall Wace Asia Limited, 23/F LHT Tower, 31 Queen’s Road, Central, Hong Kong, is licensed by the Hong Kong Securities and Futures Commission ("SFC") (CE No ANM673) for Dealing in Securities and Asset Management.

