Capital Markets

Company Overview of Marshall Wace LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Marshall Wace LLP is an employee owned hedge fund manager. The firm launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. It also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity and hedging markets across the globe. It also invests in alternative investments markets. The firm employs fundamental analysis to make its investments. It obtains external research to complement its in-house research. Marshall Wace LLP was founded in 1997 and is based in London, United Kingdom.


